{"tid":42101,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去旅行又驚又怕","createTime":"2016-12-16T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T22:00:42.000Z","uid":7278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ffb2f1ef8f91a89f525e59316dc903391de314","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"怕自己訂機票入錯一個英文字 一個數字 搞到去唔成<br />\n<br />\n所以入好資料 會對十尻幾次 望完又望對完又對 <br />\n<br />\n對到佢話超時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又會ff 可能發生嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做完回鄕證 佢話十二月三十號有 係咪真係有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b9d3e9a1df096194ed0a533f9896f54d473a82","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe9641e6bf85ac18298635ef017a1fc296ad0e0","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"又驚又怕嘅感覺 其實都係出門個種不安嘅喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未試過喺機場過夜 好撚驚驚"},{"pid":"ee16da1f8126fbed6e13702a68c38ba144dc4dcd","tid":42101,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"我有個fd都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a626acb6102dc1bc484605fcfc820334c675b0a","tid":42101,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"一日未去完個旅行都唔會放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164b8a023ed0d5e0e98f132faa6bf9f01d6fea8a","tid":42101,"uid":38492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛前一晚會失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0bb00de16c586a75a0f3324b2c7ced870112a3","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個fd都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會係你個fd 掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傻啦我都無fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ab9df036c0f14c2c069dc71a309eeb9bb6730e","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日未去完個旅行都唔會放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難將個人放鬆 明明去玩搞到。。唔識形容"},{"pid":"cd18c86bdce42d03cfd77320cea0b5b9f8d428ae","tid":42101,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛前一晚會失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前一晩諗  呀我廿四個鐘後喺邊度個度<br />\n<br />\n好怕因為意外 天氣 影響自己預期行程<br />\n雖然行程我無好仔細諗"},{"pid":"a97c3e47ce1650fc4f60ef8f875b8aec128f2ce6","tid":42101,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"機票一定望多幾次<br />\n自己唔係穩陣嘅人 同埋Murphy's law<br />\n錯得嘅一定會錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過唔記得帶身份證<br />\n而家一定有個check list比自己"},{"pid":"fff7b99dee5d2de8383a258536d7e5a07c48b20b","tid":42101,"uid":66714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"次次去旅行之前都會好多憂慮<br />\n買咩都好似精神緊張咁 又驚有咩意外<br />\n但最後次次都會覺得時間好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1437039fb6dd6c4ee3505d1442b95f2a4371d9d5","tid":42101,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci